Configuration options:

log_dir         location of primary logs
                default: current directory
img_name        name of image file
                default: out.img
img_size        size of image in mb
                default: 2000
base_dir        directory to hold image file
                default: current directory
fs_type         filesystem type for image
                default: ext2
fs_options      options to pass to mkfs
                default: (none)
jobs            number of parallel make jobs
                default: (none)
dl_dir          location of saved downloads
                default: (none)
arch            image architecture (do not change)
                default: x86_64
save            save incomplete image
                default: 0 (no)
mount_options   options to pass when mounting iso
                default: (none)
core            core packageset to install
                default: base
